# 跨 OS 行尾规范化：入库统一 LF，检出按平台。防止 Windows 提交时整文件“全变更”噪音。
* text=auto eol=lf

# Unix 脚本即使在 Windows 检出也必须保持 LF
*.sh    text eol=lf

# Windows 脚本保持 CRLF
*.ps1   text eol=crlf
*.psm1  text eol=crlf
*.bat   text eol=crlf
*.cmd   text eol=crlf

# 二进制：不碰行尾、不按文本 diff
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.pdf   binary
